title: True Transmogrification
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

You transmogrify your eidolon each day. 

During your daily preparations, you can swap out any number of your evolution feats, each for a different evolution feat of an appropriate level for which you meet the prerequisites.

These swaps last until your next daily preparations.